data.description: Come experience this beautiful Lennar home in the highly sought after Bridgeland Subdivision.  This home has a spacious island kitchen with 42" cabinets, stainless appliances, and granite countertops.  All wet areas have tile; wood floors in the entry, dining, study, kitchen, breakfast and family rooms.  Cast stone fireplace. A large primary bedroom and primary bathroom with jetted tub and separate stand-alone shower.  This is a Energy Star home. The masterplan community offers beautiful waterways, parks, pools, tennis, basketball courts, soccer fields, walking trails, community event areas, and so much more.  Convenient shopping, excellent schools and nearby entrance to highway and tollways.  This property want last!!!
